<emphasis id="B96F2764FFFF3129FF6982FAFF16ADEE" box="[132,179,1493,1519]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="12">Style</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BA4FB76FFFF3129FF6982DAFDC8AE0E" blockId="5.[132,621,1493,1551]" box="[132,621,1525,1551]" pageId="5" pageNumber="12">
Jaune; stigmates inclus puis exserts de 
<quantity id="4CE35693FFFF3129FDC982DAFDCCAE0E" box="[548,617,1525,1551]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.0" pageId="5" pageNumber="12" unit="mm" value="4.0">4 mm</quantity>
.
</paragraph>
</subSection>
<subSection id="E294E29DFFFF3129FF69811AFF6EAE4E" box="[132,203,1589,1615]" pageId="5" pageNumber="12" type="multiple">
