<heading id="D0EC4C1AFFFF3129FF69817AFE9FAE6E" box="[132,314,1620,1647]" fontSize="11" level="6" pageId="5" pageNumber="12" reason="1">
Jaune 3 × 
<quantity id="4CE35693FFFF3129FF1F817BFE92AE6E" box="[242,311,1620,1647]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.0" pageId="5" pageNumber="12" unit="mm" value="2.0">2 mm</quantity>
.
</heading>
</paragraph>
</subSection>
<subSection id="E294E29DFFFF3129FF6981BAFCADAECF" pageId="5" pageNumber="12" type="multiple">
