<quantity id="4CE35693FFFF3129FE95803BFE18AF2F" box="[376,445,1812,1838]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.0" pageId="5" pageNumber="12" unit="mm" value="3.0">3 mm</quantity>
, ovales, à arêtes très arrondies, sans ailettes.
</paragraph>
</subSection>
